@node draco "Klon AMIGI"



* Nowy KLON Amigi nazywa sië "DraCo" i jest produktem firmy
  MacroSystem z Niemiec na bazie procesora 68060.
 Technical data:
  - Processor:  Motorola 68060
  - Operating System:  Amiga OS & various UNIX Systems
  - Case:  Full size tower
  - I/O:  Fast SCSI-II with NCR 53C720 & Parallel Port
  - Slots: Two DraCo direct 32 bit interfaces dedicated for the Retina
    BLT and VLab Motion. The retina is standard in every computer, the
    VLab motion is optional. Five Zorro II slots for boards like the 
    Toccata, Emplant, Ethernet, VLab Y/C, serial ports, additional 
    parallel ports, etc.
  - Drive: Triple speed CD ROM drive standard, other SCSI devices optional
  - Graphics:  DraCo Retina BLT with 120 MHz pixel frequency and data rate
    of over 180MB/Second in 24 bit
  - Memory:  4MB standard, expandable to 128MB
  - Software Compatibility:  All system compatible programs that runs on
    graphics cards like the Retina will work.
  - Hardware Compatibility:  All hardware products that are custom chipset
    independent. This includes the Toccata, Emplant, etc.
 
